@hbuddz 
This kind of detection is called false positives; false positives (false alarms) are harmless files or URLs that are incorrectly identified as malicious by the antivirus program.

The script is open source and anyone can verify that there is no malicious code. You can also look into manual activation process https://massgrave.dev/hwid.html#Manual_Activation

